      <b>
       th mnmlsm f vgnsm
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       Ths pst wll strk  nrv wth sm rdrs, s mny mnmlsts r sprng mnmlsts r d-hrd crnvrs. Thy lv thr mt nd dn’t wnt t hr nythng gnst t.
      </p>
      <p>
       Wll, hr m t, pls. If y cld rd t th nd f th pst bfr dsgrng, blstng m, r dsmssng m, I’d b grtfl.
      </p>
      <p>
       In ths pst I’ll tll y (brfly) why I chs vgnsm nd hw t s th dt I blv s mst n ln wth mnmlsm.
      </p>
      <h3>
       Mnml tng
      </h3>
      <p>
       Vgnsm, smply dfnd, s bstnng frm nml prdcts, frm mt nd fsh nd pltry t dry nd ggs nd thr sch prdcts. I ls try fr whl fds tht r mnmlly prcssd, whch mns I mstly t vggs, frts, nts, sds, bns, sm whl grns.
      </p>
      <p>
       Ths s  lmtd, mnml dt, nd yt t cn b ncrdbly stsfyng nd mxmlly flvrfl. It’s ls vry hlthy, vry lght, nd lw n th bdgt (f y cmpr t t tng whl fds crnvrsly).
      </p>
      <p>
       A smll mnt f ngrdnts. Lght n th plt nd stmch. Esy t prpr, wth  mnmm f fss.
       <span id="more-590">
       </span>
      </p>
      <h3>
       Th mst sstnbl dt
      </h3>
      <p>
       I wn’t g nt th fgrs hr (thy’r
       <a href="http://www.vegansociety.com/References/Environment.aspx">
        cvrd
       </a>
       <a href="http://www.veganoutreach.org/whyvegan/environment.html">
        bttr
       </a>
       <a href="http://www.enviroveggie.com/">
        lswhr
       </a>
       ), bt rsng nmls fr mt, ggs nd dry s ncrdbly wstfl. Fr vry pnd f mt r dry, mny tms tht mnt f plnts mst b sd t fd th nmls fr ths prdcts.
      </p>
      <p>
       Anmls ls prdc  hg mnt f plltn nd
       <a href="http://www.goveg.com/environment-globalWarming.asp">
        cntrbt mmnsly t grnhs gss
       </a>
       , nt t mntn th mchnry nd fl tht’s sd t rs, slghtr nd trnsprt thm … nd ll th plnts ndd t fd thm. Thy cntrbt hgly t
       <a href="http://www.mcspotlight.org/media/reports/beyond.html#3">
        dfrsttn nd thr nvrnmntl prblms
       </a>
       s wll.
      </p>
      <p>
       Etng nly plnts cts tht wst t  mnml mnt, nd s s mch bttr fr th nvrnmnt. Mnmlsts wh cr bt lvng lghtly nd sstnbly wld d wll t
       <a href="http://www.vegan.org/about_veganism/environment.html">
        rsrch ths
       </a>
       nd cnsdr t.
      </p>
      <h3>
       Mnml crlty
      </h3>
      <p>
       On f th mn rsns fr bcmng  vgn s tht w dn’t blv nmls shld b hld cptv, sffr, nd b slghtrd fr r plsr.
      </p>
      <p>
       Thr s bsltly n nd fr hmns t cnsm nml prdcts t lv  hlthy lf. Sr, w’v tn thm fr mllns f yrs, bt s mllns nd mllns f ppl hv prvn, y cn t  vgn dt nd b hlthy.
      </p>
      <p>
       And s, th nly rsn t t nml prdcts s plsr — y lk th tst nd “cn’t gv t p”. Vgns dn’t blv nmls shld sffr fr r plsr, nd bcmng vgn mns y’r ptng t f  scty tht trts nmls wth xtrm crlty nd prtnds t dsn’t hppn.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Addndm 1
       </strong>
       : Obvsly ths ppls t fctry frmng, bt t’s ls tr f fr-rng, grss-fd nmls. Sm vgns (myslf ncldd) dn’t blv nmls r bjcts tht shld b sd fr r plsr, kpt cptv nd klld, n mttr hw “hmnly” w trt thm whl lv. Ths s kn t slvry f  fllw thnkng, flng crtr. Anmls dn’t xst fr hmn bnft — thy xst fr thr wn bnft.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Addndm 2
       </strong>
       : Anthr jstfctn cmmnly md s tht vgtrns kll plnts, nd ths r lvng thngs t. Hwvr, thy dn’t fl nd thnk nd sffr n th sm wy tht hmns nd nmls d — thy dn’t hv  cntrl nrvs systm r brn. It’s  fllcs rgmnt — crnvrs hv n prblm wth kllng plnts, nd r nly pntng ths t t mk vgns lk ncnsstnt. If y fl tht kllng plnts s crl, thn I chllng y t lv cnsstntly wth tht blf. Vgns r dng r bst t lv cnsstntly wth rs.
      </p>
      <h3>
       Lvng lghtly, nt lwys cnvnntly
      </h3>
      <p>
       If yr dfntn f mnmlsm nvlvs lwys chsng th mst cnvnnt, sst ptns, thn vgnsm mght nt b th mst mnml chc. It cn smtms b ncnvnnt, whn tng t rstrnts tht rn’t vgn-frndly r t th hms f nn-vgn frnds r fmly.
      </p>
      <p>
       Tht’s  rlty, bt n trth, t’s nt tht hrd. I mstly ck my wn fd, wth  mnmm f prprtn, nd s mst dys I hv n prblms whtsvr.
      </p>
      <p>
       Mr nd mr rstrnts r bcmng vgn-frndly, nd th ns tht rn’t cn slly whp p  qck nd smpl vgtbl dsh n rqst. I slly vd McDnld’s nd mst fst fd nywy. Whn I g t smn ls’s hs, I slly brng  dsh wth m, nd frnds nd fmly wh knw m bst ftn wll ck  dsh fr m t f cnsdrtn.
      </p>
      <p>
       S t’s nt tht hrd. My sggstn, f y’r ntrstd, s strtng smll: try
       <a href="http://zenhabits.posterous.com/leos-healthy-scrambled-tofu">
        cpl
       </a>
       <a href="http://zenhabits.net/2007/03/recipe-best-soup-ever/">
        vgn dshs
       </a>
       ths wk,
       <a href="http://zenhabits.net/2007/02/health-tip-try-eating-vegetarian/">
        cpl
       </a>
       nxt wk, nd
       <a href="http://zenhabits.posterous.com/my-favorite-healthy-breakfast">
        s n
       </a>
       . Thr’s n nd t drstclly chng vrnght, bt n tm y’ll fnd tht vgn dshs r dlcs nd th vgn lfstyl s wndrflly mnmlst.
